reviewText: While I didn't get this here, I bought one of the others here. If you are looking for good tornado footage, this one, like the other two, is excellent, and makes me wish that these Tornado Video Classics I, II and III were on DVD so that I can still view these videos. From a historical context these films are quite informative and the scenes are spectacularly done. These don't necessarily concentrate on the chasers, but rather, what they are doing and what they are seeing, which is a huge plus.
